    "Clever Kitten primarily targets global companies with strategic importance to countries that are contrary to Iranian interests.<br /><br />Clever Kitten actors have a strong affinity for PHP server-side attacks to make access; this is relatively unique amongst targeted attackers who often favor targeting a specific individual at a specific organization using social engineering. Some attackers have moved to leveraging strategic web compromises. The reason for this is likely the availability of exploits against web browsers, which for a variety of reasons allows an attacker to bypass security features such as Data Execution Prevention",
    "or Address Space Layout Randomization",
    ".</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Sectors: Global companies with strategic importance to countries that are contrary to Iranian interests..</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=Acunetix%20Web%20Vulnerability%20Scanner\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use Acunetix Web Vulnerability Scanner\" class=\"inlink\">Acunetix Web Vulnerability Scanner</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=RC%20SHELL\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use RC SHELL\" class=\"inlink\">RC SHELL</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://www.crowdstrike.com/blog/whois-clever-kitten/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.crowdstrike.com/blog/whois-clever-kitten/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 14 April 2020</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Clever%20Kitten&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Clever%20Kitten&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\